ðŸ”¹â‘  Problem	: Japanese Cities Attributes
	Task: Query all columns (attributes) of every Japanese city in the CITY table. COUNTRYCODE for Japan is JPN.
Solution 
		SELECT *  FROM CITY 
		WHERE COUNTRYCODE = 'JPN'

